::GoldenEye:: 

She walked over and looked at Phobia. "He's right.  We need a leader 
right now.  KitKat said for us to join the Allience.  I agree with 
her.  It would give us reenforsements for a time and give us a safe 
place to stay for a while."

She looked down and heard KitKat speak. "Terrosaur?  You want 
Terrorsaur to lead this group?"  She closed her eyes and shook her 
head. She then looked up at the others.  "Well, you heard her guys. I 
guess Terrorsaur is leading us for now."

She walked over and put her arms around Dollen's waist.  She looked
at 
Terrorsaur. "I guess your it, Leader."

She smiled at Dollen and kissed his cheek,"Well, at least we aren't 
under attack."
